I bought this dvd to see if the rumors and speculation was true about Night Shift Nurses. What they said was true. A psychotic doctor performs sick experiments for his demented pleasure on innocent nurses, in some cases, it damages the nurses psychie. Most notably of these experiments involve forced defecation (which caught me by surprise and made me woozy). It also has that chilling factor for those who are into suspense. If you're into this sorta thing, Night Shift Nurses maybe for you.
